---

<Layout>
  <GalleryItem source={winter_campfire} title="Algonquin" description="Boiling snow to make tea" />
  <GalleryItem source={magpie_falls} title="Scenic High Falls" description="Sometimes colours are just a distraction" />
  <GalleryItem source={elfin_lakes_one} title="Elfin Lakes" description="This is how I introduced my friends to backpacking" />
  <GalleryItem source={stormhaven} title="Stormhaven" description="Camping in November has many perks" />
  <GalleryItem source={highlands_backpacking} title="Highlands Trail" description="How can a loop trail be all uphill?" />
  <GalleryItem source={sinclair_cove} title="Sinclair Cove" description="Whoops, I dropped my hiking poles off of the side" />
  <GalleryItem source={flowerpot} title="Seawall" description="There's something terrifying about the grandness of the Pacific Ocean" />
  <GalleryItem source={nokomis_bay} title="Nokomis Bay" description="The northern coastline of Lake Superior always feels like a dream to me" />
  <GalleryItem source={library} title="Vancouver" description="Knowledge and gladitorial skills are both sources of power" />
